The 2019 MyBroadband Cloud Conference and Expo will be hosted on 6 June 2019 at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand, Gauteng. The event will showcase the latest products and services from South Africa’s premier cloud, hosting, data centre, and cloud telecoms providers. All delegates will also receive a voucher booklet with special deals and promotions on cloud and hosting products and services for their business. Radio 702’s Aki Anastasiou will serve as emcee for the conference, and he will share the stage with South Africa’s top cloud and hosting experts. Liquid Telecom CEO Reshaad Sha will deliver the keynote address, followed by Connection Telecom MD David Meintjes, and Microsoft Axiz’s Kevin George. Delegates will also hear from Teraco CFO Jan Hnizdo, VMWare’s Dave Funnell, Google Cloud specialist Brett StClair, and Schneider Electric’s Derek Friend. In addition to this, the conference will feature discussions about moving your business to the cloud, involving experts from SAP, Oracle, and Mimecast. MyBroadband readers can register for the conference at a big discount using the voucher code below. Please note that only 47 tickets are still available at this discounted rate, after which the standard rate will apply. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-307152" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors.jpg" alt="Cloud-Conference-Sponsors" width="640" height="1582" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors.jpg 1280w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors-162x400.jpg 162w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors-768x1898.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors-174x430.jpg 174w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cloud-Conference-Sponsors-1200x2965.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 90